The season is over and it’s very bittersweet ! 🥺

To @daniellenstamper thank you so much for this opportunity I’m forever grateful ! Our quick conversation about your plans for the upcoming season that turned into a job offer. Lots of planning and long days but every game the girls ATE ! From head to toe. So glad I was able to work with you and to have the friendship we have formed. Thank you for trusting me with your girls ❤️ @jayphine & @scooter_renee i love y’all too ! I can’t thank y’all enough for the way I was welcomed in 🫶🏾

To the Motion @officialtsumotion thank you for trusting and opening up to a complete stranger to do your hair every week not even knowing what my work looked like! I have never laughed so much than when I’m around y’all !The bonds and friendships I have formed with this talented group of ladies is so amazing ! Until next season 〽️❤️🌊
